{"about_the_game":"Lead your people to their new settlement in this survival city-builder. You will need to provide their shelter, guarantee the food supply, protect against threats of nature, and pay attention to well-being, happiness, education, and employment. Do all of this well, and you might even attract residents from foreign cities! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/FindYourHome.png?t=1730256235\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/Gif_1_-_Carving.gif?t=1730256235\" /><br><br>Choose where to build your settlement based on nearby resources, before determining your perfect layout. How will you build your settlement?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/ShapeTheLandscape.png?t=1730256235\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/img6.gif?t=1730256235\" /><br><br>Carve out the land, join rivers, form lakes and use your tools to shape your settlement exactly how you want it.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/ExpandYourPopulation.png?t=1730256235\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/Gif_6_-_Building_New.gif?t=1730256235\" /><br><br>Build housing, recruit Mayors to determine the morality of your settlement, control crime and ensure your baby-booms don\u2019t negatively impact your resources. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/SurviveTheElements.png?t=1730256235\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/Gif_2_-_Disasters.gif?t=1730256235\" /><br><br>Experience all seasons and heed the early warning signs of disasters. Bunker down and protect your citizens from the elements as well as environmental disasters, or risk losing all that you\u2019ve built.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/DiscoverRareBlueprints.png?t=1730256235\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/Gif_3_-_Mega_Buildings.gif?t=1730256235\" /><br><br>Offering powerful effects, unique themes and styles, rare blueprints are an opportunity to customize your settlement even further when you\u2019ve mastered the art of trading.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/ChooseTheRightRoutes.png?t=1730256235\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/keji_en.gif?t=1730256235\" /><br><br>Determine which development routes you will choose, with options that range from trading, education, mining, construction, agriculture, processing, logistics, and liveability. Each route unlocks new buildings and abilities to boost development. and there is no set pattern to the route selection, so you can choose freely and play to your strengths.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/ExploreUniqueMaps.png?t=1730256235\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/Gif_7_-_Fly_By.gif?t=1730256235\" /><br><br>With each map randomly generated, right down to its resources and landmarks, every experience is unique and brings with it its own challenges.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/DevelopYourTrade.png?t=1730256235\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/Gif_8_-_Boat_Trade.gif?t=1730256235\" /><br><br>Whether exchanging artistic items of high value, unprocessed products or unlocking the mint to create a common currency, trade is key to your populations survival.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/ReliveHistoricalMoments.png?t=1730256235\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/Relive.gif?t=1730256235\" /><br><br>Experience a unique game mode designed to challenge even the most experienced player. From the bubonic plague in Europe, to the Easter Island disaster, are you able to overcome its challenges?","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Agriculture Tycoon","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1509510/883212a1f11c26a407509a6322b55b6934150fe1.jpg"},{"name":"Prosperity","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1509510/c1b7267f33ba5210b3ca1df8a5941b20f4b68fa7.jpg"},{"name":"Treatment of plague","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1509510/19bd23ef586e2e5139210260ac597567a3422f7e.jpg"},{"name":"Happiness Maintainer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1509510/19ee7e56b41e9789f86e2c5bf3061c10fff8e3e2.jpg"},{"name":"Against the Cold","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1509510/23798c40cfe6ce07d3ad90fe15790b5d6bb060e7.jpg"},{"name":"Skilled Workers","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1509510/4b07024e252336b00fe5bdec80a46f0d686aaeec.jpg"},{"name":"Advanced Technology","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1509510/efed876e55bbeed0651bc9048f680a8172789913.jpg"},{"name":"Civilized Land","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1509510/53176bbc136d78369274866aaa5b73a41e387da7.jpg"},{"name":"Thorough Cleaning","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1509510/9e4909fc45c6a2b7449f1bde6e2b017a46335f1b.jpg"},{"name":"Animal Imports","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1509510/a5685dc2fef22aa0b2360267d82318f874847848.jpg"}],"total":51},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730256235","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/page.bg.jpg?t=1730256235","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730256235","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730256235","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Steam Workshop","id":30},{"description":"Steam Cloud","id":23},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h1>Discord</h1><p><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/Discord.png?t=1730256235\" /></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Lead your people to their new settlement in this survival city-builder. You will need to provide their shelter, guarantee the food supply, protect against threats of nature, and pay attention to well-being, happiness, education, and employment. Do all of this well, and you might even attract residents from foreign cities! <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/FindYourHome.png?t=1730256235\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/Gif_1_-_Carving.gif?t=1730256235\" /><br><br>Choose where to build your settlement based on nearby resources, before determining your perfect layout. How will you build your settlement?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/ShapeTheLandscape.png?t=1730256235\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/img6.gif?t=1730256235\" /><br><br>Carve out the land, join rivers, form lakes and use your tools to shape your settlement exactly how you want it.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/ExpandYourPopulation.png?t=1730256235\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/Gif_6_-_Building_New.gif?t=1730256235\" /><br><br>Build housing, recruit Mayors to determine the morality of your settlement, control crime and ensure your baby-booms don\u2019t negatively impact your resources. <br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/SurviveTheElements.png?t=1730256235\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/Gif_2_-_Disasters.gif?t=1730256235\" /><br><br>Experience all seasons and heed the early warning signs of disasters. Bunker down and protect your citizens from the elements as well as environmental disasters, or risk losing all that you\u2019ve built.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/DiscoverRareBlueprints.png?t=1730256235\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/Gif_3_-_Mega_Buildings.gif?t=1730256235\" /><br><br>Offering powerful effects, unique themes and styles, rare blueprints are an opportunity to customize your settlement even further when you\u2019ve mastered the art of trading.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/ChooseTheRightRoutes.png?t=1730256235\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/keji_en.gif?t=1730256235\" /><br><br>Determine which development routes you will choose, with options that range from trading, education, mining, construction, agriculture, processing, logistics, and liveability. Each route unlocks new buildings and abilities to boost development. and there is no set pattern to the route selection, so you can choose freely and play to your strengths.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/ExploreUniqueMaps.png?t=1730256235\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/Gif_7_-_Fly_By.gif?t=1730256235\" /><br><br>With each map randomly generated, right down to its resources and landmarks, every experience is unique and brings with it its own challenges.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/DevelopYourTrade.png?t=1730256235\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/Gif_8_-_Boat_Trade.gif?t=1730256235\" /><br><br>Whether exchanging artistic items of high value, unprocessed products or unlocking the mint to create a common currency, trade is key to your populations survival.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/ReliveHistoricalMoments.png?t=1730256235\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/extras/Relive.gif?t=1730256235\" /><br><br>Experience a unique game mode designed to challenge even the most experienced player. From the bubonic plague in Europe, to the Easter Island disaster, are you able to overcome its challenges?","developers":["Gleamer Studio"],"dlc":[2511170,3061350],"genres":[{"description":"Simulation","id":"28"},{"description":"Strategy","id":"2"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509510/header.jpg?t=1730256235","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> OS X 10.11 (64-bit)<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core 2 Duo, 3.0GHz/Apple  M1<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 4 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> nVIDIA GeForce GTX 260, 512 MB or ATI Radeon HD 5670, 512 MB<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 2 GB available space</li></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> OS X 10.11 (64-bit)<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Intel Core i5-3470, 3.20GHz/Apple  M2<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 6 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> nVIDIA GeForce GTX 660, 2 GB or AMD Radeon HD 7870, 2 GB<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 2 GB available space</li></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":256854049,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256854049/movie480.mp4?t=1669945905","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256854049/movie_max.mp4?t=1669945905"},"name":"Settlement Survival -2","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/256854049/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1669945905","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256854049/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1669945905","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/256854049/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1669945905"}},{"highlight":true,"id":2